			<h3 ><a href="#p4034" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: Projecting the Orioles' 2012 Starting Rotation<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=4034&amp;sid=879fda5af19459ac45bf0771e2327a0e#p4034"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=4034&amp;sid=879fda5af19459ac45bf0771e2327a0e#p4034" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#38</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=879fda5af19459ac45bf0771e2327a0e" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; October 5th, 2011, 4:31 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

